quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,"Yeewtere sugu mun yawtii ka arannde cortewol Baqarah."
  7,2,"Alqur'aanaare Teddunde nden, ko Deftere Jippinaande e maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- Wata …ìitteende fii mayre wonu ka …ìernde maa ; Alla Jippiniriinde e maa…óa fii jertinirgol nde yim…ìe …ìen, √±ii…ìiniraande hujja, e fii yo a waajornde gom…óim…ìe …ìen ; ko …ìen nafitorta waaju."
  7,3,"Jokkee onon …ìee yim…ìe, Deftere nde Joomi mon Jippini e moo…óon e sunna Annabiijo mon on, wata on jokku mbelee…óe …ìen …ìe sikkoton ko weldii…ìe mo'on -immorde e seytaaneeji maa ruu…óinkinii…ìe- Kono fan…óii ko waajitoto…óon ; tawde si on waajitino, on …ìurnataano go…ó…óum goo e goonga kan, on jokkayno ko Nulaa…óo mon on addani on kon, gollitiron …óum, hawkon ko lunndii …óum."
  7,4,"∆äuu…ói e ca'e …óe Men halkiri lepte Amen! ∆Åaawo nde …ìe ha…ì…ìitii e keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe, Men Jppini lepte Amen …óen e ma…ì…ìe fewndo ka …ìe welsindii jemma maa √±alorma, …ìe waawaano yiltude …óen e ma…ì…ìe, rewetee…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin kadi nafaano …ìe e …óum."
  7,5,"∆Åaawo lepte …óen arii e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wa…óaano si wanaa qirritagol e ko'e ma…ì…ìe, wonnde …ìe too√±irno yeddugol Alla."
  7,6,"Ma Men Lamnditoyo √ëalnde Darngal, mofte …óe Men Nulunoo …óen e mun Nulaa…ìe fii ko …ìe jaabitinoo Nulaa…ìe …ìen, Ma Men Lamnditoyo kadi Nulaa…ìe …ìen si …ìe yottinnno Nule …óen e si tawii …ìe mofte ma…ì…ìe …óen jaabitino …ìe."
  7,7,"Ma Men Fillanoyor tagu ngun fow golle ma…ì…ìe …óen aduna, e hoore ganndal Amen ; tawde gom…óii Me…óen Anndunoo …óum, huunde e mun wirnaaki Men, Men wonaano kadi welsindii…ìe e kala waqtu."
  7,8,"Manndake …óen √ëalnde Darngal, ko e nun…óal …óe manndikirtee wanaa too√±e. kala mo manndake mun mo∆¥∆¥i …óen teddi …ìuri bon…ói …óin, ko …ìen …óon woni maloytee…ìe …ìen."
  7,9,"Kala mo manndake mon mo∆¥∆¥i …óen foygitii …ìuri bon…ói makko …óin, ko …ìen …óon woni sooyinir…ìe pittaali mun …óin halkagol √ëalnde Darngal, sabu ko …ìe yeddaynoo Aayeeje Alla …óen."
  7,10,"Gom…óii Men Newinanii on -onon …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama …ìen- ka leydi. Men Wa…óani on nguuree e mayri. Tawi ko yettugol Alla tun habbora…óon, kono fan…óii ko yettoton."
  7,11,"Gom…óii Men Tagii baaba mon Aadama, hooti Men Mbaadiniri mo ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e mbaadi, hooti Men Yamiri Mala'ik'en sujjirangol mo teddungal, …ìe …óoftii …ìe sujji, si wanaa Ibliisa, o salora sujjungol towonitaare."